      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AjHxP2fneLRBmi0HSutjO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -318.3489583333361,
      "y": 1029.0083705357151,
      "width": 328.7797546386719,
      "height": 500,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "am",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1718555064,
      "version": 455,
      "versionNonce": 1907116232,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772655889230,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When you create an issue:\n- create a Message message = {\n    .author = agent | user\n    .body = <the text> \n    .timestamp = now()\n    .seen = null\n}\n- Create a Response response = {\n    .content = message,\n    .responding_to = null\n    .response = null\n    .reply = null\n}\n- create an Issue issue = {\n    .inum = 42,\n    .group = \"\",\n    .block_by = []\n    .blocks = []\n    .body = response\n}",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When you create an issue:\n- create a Message message = {\n    .author = agent | user\n    .body = <the text> \n    .timestamp = now()\n    .seen = null\n}\n- Create a Response response = {\n    .content = message,\n    .responding_to = null\n    .response = null\n    .reply = null\n}\n- create an Issue issue = {\n    .inum = 42,\n    .group = \"\",\n    .block_by = []\n    .blocks = []\n    .body = response\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "d9-VfwrVt7non_NrRwErt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -818.6549479166688,
      "y": 1432.3351934523816,
      "width": 514.2596435546875,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "an",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 322304456,
      "version": 384,
      "versionNonce": 574592440,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772655888610,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "when you reply to a Response: \n- create a Message message = {\n    .author = agent | user\n    .body = <the text> \n    .timestamp = now()\n    .seen = null\n}\n- create a Response new_response = {\n    .content = message,\n    .responding_to = the Response being replied to\n    .response = null\n    .reply = null\n}\n- update theResponseBeingRepliedTo.reply:\n    theResponseBeingRepliedTo.reply = new_response",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "when you reply to a Response: \n- create a Message message = {\n    .author = agent | user\n    .body = <the text> \n    .timestamp = now()\n    .seen = null\n}\n- create a Response new_response = {\n    .content = message,\n    .responding_to = the Response being replied to\n    .response = null\n    .reply = null\n}\n- update theResponseBeingRepliedTo.reply:\n    theResponseBeingRepliedTo.reply = new_response",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5IcKpx0McZpSlAtN0ZhSS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -295.79036458333576,
      "y": 1559.6672247023816,
      "width": 547.919677734375,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ao",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 325298120,
      "version": 655,
      "versionNonce": 205823432,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772655889788,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When you add a response to an issue: \n- create a Message message = {\n    .author = agent | user\n    .body = <the text> \n    .timestamp = now()\n    .seen = null\n}\n- Create a Response new_response = {\n    .content = message,\n    .responding_to = the end of the Response linked-list\n    .response = null\n    .reply = null\n}\n- find the last Response node in the issue: \nlastResponseNode = issue.body\nwhile( lastResponseNode != null )\n    if( lastResponseNode.response == null )\n        break;\n    lastResponseNode = lastResponseNode.response \n- add the new_response to the lastResponseNode. \nlastResponseNode.response = new_response",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When you add a response to an issue: \n- create a Message message = {\n    .author = agent | user\n    .body = <the text> \n    .timestamp = now()\n    .seen = null\n}\n- Create a Response new_response = {\n    .content = message,\n    .responding_to = the end of the Response linked-list\n    .response = null\n    .reply = null\n}\n- find the last Response node in the issue: \nlastResponseNode = issue.body\nwhile( lastResponseNode != null )\n    if( lastResponseNode.response == null )\n        break;\n    lastResponseNode = lastResponseNode.response \n- add the new_response to the lastResponseNode. \nlastResponseNode.response = new_response",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
